  "texts": [
    "In the left case, AutoSDhypothesizes that the bug is happening when the current token is END_OBJECT, and generates an experiment to confirm that this is the case.",
    "As this is actually the case, it proceeds to search for what behavior would lead to the failing test to pass in Attempt 2.",
    "Combining these two steps together, it generates a patch identical (in this method) to the developer patch, and that makes all tests in the test suite pass.",
    "Meanwhile, on the right, another example of failing to identify the right breakpoint is provided.",
    "In this case, the same hypothesis and experiments are parroted, leading to no improvement."
